{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Remember the classic sim city builder games that took you so long to figure out how to successfully create a town from scratch that can later be self sufficient to run properly on its own!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">That brought about the idea of Just Build. It is a simplified version of those games without all the complexity but focuses more on time management and resource management.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3341220/extras/gif1.1.gif?t=1734878798\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Just Build focuses on:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Time Management</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In just Build, you have a set of objectives which you have to complete within a particular amount of time like for example, having a population  of over 200 before 10 minutes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3341220/extras/gif3.gif?t=1734878798\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Resource Management:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Just Build, Resource management is very important because completing the objectives depend solely on how you managed your resources.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3341220/extras/gif2.1.gif?t=1734878798\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Just Build is being created by a solo developer, so it's not a blockbuster experience but what I'd like to offer you is a simple game that challenges you to create little towns within a short period of time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragra